OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FMost complaints made about the States
OL,7,Fof Jersey Police last year concerned
OL,8,Falleged abuses of authority.
OL,10,FThese grievances made up nine of the
OL,11,F17 cases referred to the independent
OL,12,FJersey Police Complaints Commission
OL,13,F(JPCC) in 2025 - the joint highest
OL,14,Famount in the last five years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
