OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FThe others were two instances
OL,7,Finvolving a serious injury, two
OL,8,Falleging data protection breaches, one
OL,9,Fclaiming an excessive use of force,
OL,10,Fand three about how investigations
OL,11,Fwere handled - including one of
OL,12,Falleged sex discrimination and
OL,13,Fmedication being denied.
OL,15,FThe JPCC acts as a watchdog to oversee
OL,16,Fcomplaint investigations impartially.
OL,18,FNone of the issues concerned Honorary
OL,19,FOfficers, where over the last five
OL,20,Fyears, just six of the 66 complaints
OL,21,Fhave been against honoraries.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
