OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FOf the 17 grievances raised in 2025,
OL,7,F13 were carried forward to this year
OL,8,Fas they continued to be assessed.
OL,10,FThe other four form part of the 15
OL,11,Fcases concluded last year, which
OL,12,Fresulted in one complaint being
OL,13,Fwithdrawn, 10 marked as
OL,14,Funsubstantiated, and four partly or
OL,15,Ffully upheld.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
