CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FThese investigations took around a
OL,7,Fmonth to almost a full year to
OL,8,Fcomplete, with the JPCC recognising
OL,9,Fthat the process needs to be quicker -
OL,10,Fwhile stating that they are volunteers
OL,11,Fwho want to ensure each case is
OL,12,Fthoroughly reviewed.
OL,14,FThe report states: "The JPCC
OL,15,Frecognises all complainants have the
OL,16,Fright to be listened to, respected and
OL,17,Fhave their complaint taken seriously
OL,18,Fand investigated in a fair, impartial
OL,19,Fand independent manner."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FThe group hopes to discuss timelines
OL,7,Ffor complaints during a review of its
OL,8,FService Level Agreement this year.
OL,10,FThe number of incidents involving
OL,11,Fofficers using tasers also more than
OL,12,Fdoubled last year.
OL,14,FThere were 25 cases in 2025, with the
OL,15,Ftaser being fired three times,
OL,16,Fcompared to 12 incidents and no
OL,17,Fdeployments in 2024.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
