CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FBoth years are much lower than 2021,
OL,7,Fwhich saw 55 cases where a taser was
OL,8,Fused and 10 times when it was actually
OL,9,Ffired.
OL,11,FIn response to the report, a
OL,12,Fspokesperson for the States of Jersey
OL,13,FPolice says: "These are matters we
OL,14,Ftake seriously and which go directly
OL,15,Fto the standards of professionalism
OL,16,Fthe public rightly expects of
OL,17,Fpolicing."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
