PN,35807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1781684279
OL,3,CAbuse of authority complaints against
OL,4,CJersey Police rise
OL,6,FThey then praised the complaints
OL,7,Fprocess and welcomed independent
OL,8,Fscrutiny, adding: "Our focus remains
OL,9,Fon learning from complaints,
OL,10,Fmaintaining high professional
OL,11,Fstandards, and ensuring we deliver a
OL,12,Ffair, respectful and accountable
OL,13,Fservice to the community."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
